OL,3,CPaul O'Grady's husband reveals
OL,4,Cheartbreaking final moments with star
OL,6,F's husband said the TV star had "the
OL,7,Fmost ordinary day" before his sudden
OL,8,Fdeath exactly one year ago.
OL,10,Fborn O'Grady, who rose to fame as
OL,11,Falter-ego Lily Savage before hosting a
OL,12,Fstring of popular TV programmes, died
OL,13,Fat his home on March 28 last year at
OL,14,Fthe age of 67.
OL,16,FHis husband Andre Portasio told the
OL,17,FDaily Mirror: "He was on wonderful
OL,18,Fform and then we settled down in the
OL,19,Fliving room and switched on the telly
OL,20,Fto catch up on Kent ITV News.
