OL,3,CPaul O'Grady's husband reveals
OL,4,Cheartbreaking final moments with star
OL,6,F"He always insisted on watching the
OL,7,Fpresenter Sangeeta (Bhabra) ` he loved
OL,8,Fher and would never allow me to put
OL,9,Fthe BBC on. It was all about ITV.
OL,11,F"He left to get some tea, and I heard
OL,12,Fthis loud bang."
OL,14,FMr Portasio said he found O'Grady
OL,15,F"lying on the floor" with a cut on his
OL,16,Fforehead.
OL,18,F"I called the ambulance and they said
OL,19,Fthe best chance to keep him alive was
OL,20,Fto do CPR.
