OL,3,CPaul O'Grady's husband reveals
OL,4,Cheartbreaking final moments with star
OL,6,F"I don't know how long it took for the
OL,7,Fambulance to arrive, but by the end I
OL,8,Fwas exhausted.
OL,10,F"At one point, they were like 'yes,
OL,11,Fhe's breathing'. I thought the
OL,12,Fnightmare was gone but it was very
OL,13,Fshort-lived, and very shortly
OL,14,Fafterwards they pronounced him dead."
OL,16,FHe added: "Somehow Paul's dog Arfur,
OL,17,Fwho is one of his favourites, escaped
OL,18,Fand he nuzzled his face as he always
OL,19,Fdid on Paul's shoulder, as if to say
OL,20,F'wake up'. It was just heartbreaking."
