OL,6,FMr Portasio and O'Grady first met in
OL,7,F2006 before marrying in an intimate
OL,8,FLondon ceremony in 2017.
OL,10,FAndre said he was marking the first
OL,11,Fanniversary with a solo trip to New
OL,12,FZealand, saying he did not want to be
OL,13,F"anywhere near my kitchen where I
OL,14,Ffound him, and be reminded of what
OL,15,Fhappened".
OL,17,FThe TV star shared a special bond with
OL,18,Fthe Queen over their love of dogs,
OL,19,Fmeeting many times and working closely
OL,20,Fin support of Battersea Dogs and Cats
OL,21,FHome.
